01:47:40.450 --> 01:47:42.450
Is this the girl you've been seeing?

01:47:42.450 --> 01:47:43.450
Yeah

01:47:43.450 --> 01:47:45.450
Yeah, Donna, Donna Maitland, what's she doing here?

01:47:45.450 --> 01:47:46.450
She's dead, Johnny

01:47:46.450 --> 01:47:56.130
She died in a car accident

01:47:56.130 --> 01:47:58.130
She was...

01:47:58.130 --> 01:48:00.130
Driving with her boyfriend

01:48:00.130 --> 01:48:02.130
And their car stalled on these railroad tracks

01:48:02.130 --> 01:48:04.130
Just out by Waterloo Road

01:48:04.130 --> 01:48:06.130
They both got out

01:48:06.130 --> 01:48:08.130
But Donna forgot her ring

01:48:08.130 --> 01:48:12.600
This school ring that her boyfriend had just given her

01:48:12.600 --> 01:48:15.920
So she went back to get it

01:48:15.920 --> 01:48:22.900
And the train came

01:48:22.900 --> 01:48:25.560
She said I had her ring

01:48:25.560 --> 01:48:26.560
She was there, Erica

01:48:26.560 --> 01:48:27.560
I swear it

01:48:27.560 --> 01:48:35.840
I mean, I talked to her

01:48:35.840 --> 01:48:39.820
She said that she wanted me to go with her

01:48:39.820 --> 01:49:11.520
And it's all because of this

01:49:11.520 --> 01:49:14.280
Run for me, Johnny

01:49:14.280 --> 01:49:15.280
I want you to come with me

01:49:15.280 --> 01:49:16.280
Look, take your stupid ring back

01:49:16.280 --> 01:49:18.280
I don't want it

01:49:18.280 --> 01:49:20.280
Don't you understand?

01:49:20.280 --> 01:49:22.280
It's you that I want

01:49:22.280 --> 01:49:24.280
You must know that by now

01:49:24.280 --> 01:49:25.280
Just... just...

01:49:25.280 --> 01:49:26.280
Just leave me alone

01:49:26.280 --> 01:49:27.280
It's time, Johnny

01:49:27.280 --> 01:49:28.280
No!

01:49:28.280 --> 01:49:29.280
Johnny?

01:49:29.280 --> 01:49:34.510
Johnny?

01:49:34.510 --> 01:49:35.510
Are you okay?

01:49:35.510 --> 01:49:43.480
Did you see her?

01:49:43.480 --> 01:49:56.520
Sit down and relax, please

01:49:56.520 --> 01:49:57.520
Yeah, okay, when the ghost comes after you

01:49:57.520 --> 01:49:59.520
Let's see if you can relax

01:49:59.520 --> 01:50:04.660
Johnny...

01:50:04.660 --> 01:50:05.660
Are you sure it's the ring

01:50:05.660 --> 01:50:07.660
That's making all this happen?

01:50:07.660 --> 01:50:08.660
What do you mean?

01:50:09.660 --> 01:50:18.240
Hello?

01:50:18.240 --> 01:50:28.080
It's for you

01:50:28.080 --> 01:50:42.520
Me?

01:50:42.520 --> 01:50:43.520
Look, this is all some kind of joke

01:50:43.520 --> 01:50:45.520
And I'm not buying it anymore, understand?

01:50:45.520 --> 01:50:47.520
This isn't funny, so just leave me alone

01:50:47.520 --> 01:50:50.540
Sorry, Johnny

01:50:50.540 --> 01:51:05.310
You still think this is all a joke?

01:51:05.310 --> 01:51:14.860
You know, maybe all she wants is a ring back

01:51:14.860 --> 01:51:19.320
Maybe I should give it to her

01:51:19.320 --> 01:51:20.320
Well, how are you gonna do that?

01:51:20.320 --> 01:51:22.320
You told her to leave you alone

01:51:22.320 --> 01:51:25.800
Well, then... then I gotta find her

01:51:25.800 --> 01:51:34.000
Oh, she's really your ghost

01:51:34.000 --> 01:51:36.000
I can think of a pretty good place to start

01:51:36.000 --> 01:52:06.480
Hey, you okay?

01:52:06.480 --> 01:52:08.480
Yeah, yeah, I'm fine

01:52:08.480 --> 01:52:10.480
Just a little jumpy, that's all

01:52:10.480 --> 01:52:12.480
You find anything?

01:52:12.480 --> 01:52:14.480
Uh, no, you...

01:52:14.480 --> 01:52:23.610
No, look at this

01:52:23.610 --> 01:52:24.610
Donna Maitland

01:52:24.610 --> 01:52:28.340
This is it, this is so grave

01:52:28.340 --> 01:52:29.340
You sure?

01:52:29.340 --> 01:52:30.340
Well, yeah, look at it

01:52:30.340 --> 01:52:32.340
How many other Donna Maitlands could there be?

01:52:32.340 --> 01:52:34.340
Well, yeah, I guess

01:52:34.340 --> 01:52:36.340
But how did you know it would be right here?

01:52:36.340 --> 01:52:37.340
I didn't

01:52:37.340 --> 01:52:38.340
I just kinda...

01:52:38.340 --> 01:52:40.340
Happened to wander away from me

01:52:40.340 --> 01:52:42.340
Get lost and trip right over it?

01:52:42.340 --> 01:52:51.570
What are you talking about?

01:52:51.570 --> 01:52:53.570
You knew exactly where she was buried, Johnny

01:52:53.570 --> 01:52:55.570
Why do you think that is?

01:52:55.570 --> 01:52:57.570
Look, I don't know what you mean

01:52:57.570 --> 01:52:59.570
Maybe you've been here before

01:52:59.570 --> 01:53:01.570
Did you ever think about that?

01:53:01.570 --> 01:53:03.570
No way, why would I have been here?

01:53:03.570 --> 01:53:04.570
I'm in a cemetery

01:53:04.570 --> 01:53:06.570
Why don't you tell me, Johnny

01:53:06.570 --> 01:53:10.080
You remember what happened

01:53:10.080 --> 01:53:12.080
The car stalled on the tracks, right?

01:53:12.080 --> 01:53:16.980
And then Donna got out

01:53:16.980 --> 01:53:18.980
But she forgot her ring

01:53:18.980 --> 01:53:21.260
Her school ring

01:53:21.260 --> 01:53:23.260
And went running back for it

01:53:23.260 --> 01:53:43.120
And then what happened, Johnny?

01:53:43.120 --> 01:53:48.000
I turned back

01:53:48.000 --> 01:53:50.000
I tried to push her out of the way

01:53:50.000 --> 01:53:56.150
But she was late

01:53:56.150 --> 01:54:04.840
And I made Linda and John

01:54:04.840 --> 01:54:19.860
It's me, isn't it?

01:54:19.860 --> 01:54:20.860
And that means I...

01:54:20.860 --> 01:54:27.150
Why don't you just tell me?

01:54:27.150 --> 01:54:29.150
Because you didn't remember

01:54:29.150 --> 01:54:31.150
You just came back from the accident

01:54:31.150 --> 01:54:33.150
And acted as if nothing had happened

01:54:33.150 --> 01:54:37.150
Johnny, I was the only one who could see you

01:54:37.150 --> 01:54:40.150
And for some really weird reason

01:54:40.150 --> 01:54:43.150
You didn't remember the accident

01:54:43.150 --> 01:54:45.150
You didn't even know you were...

01:54:45.150 --> 01:54:46.150
Dead

01:54:46.150 --> 01:54:51.960
No wonder I'm so bummed all the time

01:54:51.960 --> 01:54:58.560
So what do I do?

01:54:58.560 --> 01:55:00.560
Well, now that you know

01:55:00.560 --> 01:55:02.560
Everything's gonna be okay

01:55:02.560 --> 01:55:04.560
We can still be a family

01:55:04.560 --> 01:55:05.560
And go on living

01:55:05.560 --> 01:55:07.560
And everything will be fine

01:55:07.560 --> 01:55:12.200
Johnny, is that you?

01:55:12.200 --> 01:55:20.970
Back to me

01:55:20.970 --> 01:55:39.040
I don't think I can stay

01:55:39.040 --> 01:55:40.040
I'll be locked together

01:55:40.040 --> 01:55:44.080
It's time, Johnny

01:55:44.080 --> 01:55:47.000
After her

01:55:47.000 --> 01:55:50.310
You don't want to lose her again

01:55:50.310 --> 01:55:54.680
I'm really gonna miss you, Eric

01:55:54.680 --> 01:55:58.630
You know, you're my favorite sister

01:55:58.630 --> 01:56:01.880
I'm your only sister

01:56:01.880 --> 01:56:17.150
I love you too

01:56:17.150 --> 01:57:36.840
Always going to miss Johnny

01:57:36.840 --> 01:57:38.840
But it made her feel better to know

01:57:38.840 --> 01:57:40.840
That he was happy at last

01:57:40.840 --> 01:57:44.840
With the girl of his dreams

01:57:45.840 --> 01:57:46.840
The end

01:57:46.840 --> 01:57:48.840
Good one, Sam

01:57:48.840 --> 01:57:49.840
Cool

01:57:49.840 --> 01:57:51.840
You're a ghost and you don't know it

01:57:51.840 --> 01:57:52.840
Yeah

01:57:52.840 --> 01:57:54.840
Like you're a runt and you don't even know it

01:57:54.840 --> 01:57:56.840
I'll show you who's a runt

01:57:56.840 --> 01:58:03.010
Declare this meeting of the Midnight Society Post

01:59:03.280 --> 01:59:05.280
It is post at SNCC

01:59:05.280 --> 01:59:07.280
You can SNCC again next Saturday night

01:59:07.280 --> 01:59:08.280
On Nickelodeon

